<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak direction-ltr" data-module="govspeak">
      <div class="govspeak">
<p>The information in these guides only applies in the event of a no-deal Brexit.  You should read it only to prepare for Brexit in a no-deal scenario.  These guides provide information on the product safety and metrology regulations governing these sectors, as amended by the Product Safety and Metrology etc (Amendment etc) EU Exit Regulations 2019, and by the Product Safety, Metrology and Mutual Recognition Agreements (Amendment) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019.  These guides set out how the Government intends product safety and metrology to apply in these sectors in a no-deal Brexit. Watch this space for further amendments and confirmation of when these new arrangements take effect.</p>

